      "content": "stepping away sounds nice but i mean... i mean what if i can't just \"heal\" from this? what if the only way to actually stop hurting them is to not be a part of their lives at all? like, for good? i feel like they'd be so much happier and lighter if they didn't have to worry about my mistakes anymore.",
